Comment: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:47.47,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,I must be losing my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.02,0:22:53.82,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,I keep on trying to find a way out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.82,0:23:00.36,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,But it's ok you don't lock the door anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:10.62,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,I, you know I never go out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:17.07,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,And you know that I start to forget things
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.07,0:23:24.01,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,But it's ok they weren't essential anyway
